NUMEL is extremely dull witted - it
doesnt notice being hit. However, it
cant stand hunger for even a second. This POKMONs body is a seething
cauldron of boiling magma.

NUMEL stores magma of almost 2,200
degrees F within its body. If it gets
wet, the magma cools and hardens. In that event, the POKMONs body
grows heavy and its movements become
sluggish.

A NUMEL stores boiling magma in the hump
on its back. It is a hardy POKMON that can
transport a 220-pound load. It has served
humans at work since long ago.

Magma of almost 2,200 degrees Fahrenheit
courses through its body. When it grows
cold, the magma hardens and slows it.

Chamallot est terriblement lent desprit. Il ne remarque mme
pas quand il est touch. Il ne supporte pas davoir faim,
mme une seconde. Le corps de ce Pokmon est comparable
 un chaudron de magma bouillonnant.

Camaub ist nicht besonders helle. Es nimmt nicht einmal wahr,
wenn es getroffen wurde. Ein Hungergefhl allerdings kann es
nicht einmal eine Sekunde lang aushalten. In seinem Krper
brodelt glhend heies Magma.

Numel  estremamente tardo, tanto da non notare di essere
